                                        "},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"1 ÷ 3 = 0.333 (recurring). 0.333 (recurring) x 3 = 1 or 0.999 (recurring). Can be proved other ways too."}]},{"type":"text","text":"



